# Prytula Figma → Component → Showcase

End-to-end workflow: Figma node → React component in `web/src/design-system/` → showcase page in `web/src/showcase/` → register in `routes.ts`. **Run all three phases** unless the user asks for one phase only.

## When this rule triggers

- «Перенеси Button з Figma», «Додай ProjectCard у дизайн-систему», «Створи showcase для Hero»
- Figma URL + component name
- «Додай у дизайн-систему» / «додай у showcase»

## Prerequisites

1. **`web/src/styles/tokens.css`** exists and is imported in `web/src/main.tsx` (`npm run build:tokens`).
2. **`web/src/design-system/`** exists.
3. **`web/src/showcase/`** bootstrapped (see below) if adding showcase pages.
4. Follow **`prytula-design-system`** rule: Mapped (`--surface-*`, `--text-*`), Alias (`--space-*`, `--action-*`), app `--font-display`; never raw hex/px for colors, spacing, radii, type. `--pryt-brand-*` only inside DS if unavoidable.

## Code layout (monorepo)

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `web/src/components/` | Product UI (pages, marketing) |
| `web/src/design-system/` | Reusable DS components |
| `web/src/showcase/` | DS documentation app |
| `web/src/styles/tokens.css` | Generated CSS variables |

Showcase may import design-system; design-system must **not** import showcase or product components.

---

## Bootstrap showcase (once)

Skip if `web/src/showcase/ShowcasePage.tsx` exists.

1. **`ShowcasePage.tsx`** — sidebar from `showcaseRoutes`, main pane renders active `Component`.
2. **`routes.ts`** — source of truth for nav (`Foundations` → token pages; `Components` → component showcases).
3. **`primitives/`** — `ShowcasePageLayout`, `ShowcaseSection`, `ShowcaseGrid` (token CSS vars only).
4. **`tokens/`** — `ColorsPage`, `TypographyPage`, `SpacingPage`, `RadiusPage` (introspective: read CSS vars at runtime).
5. Wire `/showcase` route in the Vite app when ready.

Canonical showcase sections per component: **Variants** → **Sizes** (if any) → **States** → **Composition** (if needed) → **Responsive** (if needed) → **Tokens used** → **Guidelines** (if real rules exist).

Sample copy: **Ukrainian**, realistic («Підтримати», «Скасувати»).

---

## Phase 1: Figma → Component

1. **Read node** via Figma MCP (`get_design_context` or metadata + screenshot): structure, text styles, fills, variants.
2. **Map to tokens** from `prytula-design-system` rule — e.g. orange CTA → `var(--surface-action)` / `var(--action-donate)`; spacing → `var(--space-medium)`. If no match → **stop and ask**; do not invent tokens.
3. **Create** `web/src/design-system/[Name]/`:
   - `[Name].types.ts` — props / variants
   - `[Name].tsx` — component
   - `[Name].module.css` — **only** semantic CSS vars (Mapped/Alias/`--font-display`)
   - `index.ts` — barrel export
4. **Verify**: no raw hex in CSS; variants match Figma; TypeScript compiles.

---

## Phase 2: Component → Showcase

Create `web/src/showcase/components/[Name]Showcase.tsx` using primitives; import component from `../../design-system/[Name]`.

Include **Tokens used** listing Figma paths / CSS vars the component consumes.

---

## Phase 3: Navigation

Register in `web/src/showcase/routes.ts` under the right group:

- **Building blocks** — Button, Input, Tag, Chip, IconButton, Divider, Avatar
- **Cards** — ProjectCard, NewsCard, PartnerCard, ProgressCard
- **Composite** — Hero, banners, headers
- **Forms** / **Navigation** — as needed

Tell the user: `npm run dev` → open `/showcase` → pick the new entry.

---

## Token showcase pages

`web/src/showcase/tokens/*` — group `--pryt-brand-*`, Alias (`--space-*`, `--bg-*`, …), Mapped (`--surface-*`, `--text-*`, …). Keep lists in sync when `figma-variables.tsv` changes (after `npm run build:tokens`).

---

## Pitfalls

- Component without showcase or without `routes.ts` entry
- Raw hex/px «just once»
- Cross-import from design-system into showcase/product
- English placeholder copy on UA product

## Maintenance

After Figma export + `npm run build:tokens`, update token showcase groups if new variables appear. Component CSS picks up token changes via cascade — no component edits unless bindings change.
